translation: That Thou art the Greatest Friend. That Thou art certainlyhe Giver of food.123.

gurmukhi: ਅਨੇਕੁਲ ਤਰੰਗ ਹੈਂ || ਅਭੇਦ ਹੈਂ ਅਭੰਗ ਹੈਂ ||
transliteration: Anekul Taran Hain|| Abhed Hain Abhan Hain||
translation: That Thou, as Ocean, Hast innumerable waves. That Thou art Immortal and none can know Thy secrets.

gurmukhi: ਅਜੀਜੁਲ ਨਿਵਾਜ ਹੈਂ || ਗਨੀਮੁਲ ਖਿਰਾਜ ਹੈਂ ||੧੨੪||
transliteration: Azoozul Nivaaz Hain|| Ghanoomul Khiraaj Hain||124||
translation: That Thou Protectest the devotees. That Thou punishest the evil-doers.124.

gurmukhi: ਨਿਰੁਕਤ ਸਰੂਪ ਹੈਂ || ਤਿ੍ਰਮੁਕਤਿ ਬਿਭੂਤ ਹੈਂ ||
translation: That Thy Entity is Indexpressible. That Thy Glory is Beyond the three Modes.

gurmukhi: ਪ੍ਰਭੁਗਤਿ ਪ੍ਰਭਾ ਹੈਂ || ਸੁ ਜੁਗਤਿ ਸੁਧਾ ਹੈਂ ||੧੨੫||
transliteration: Prabhougad(i) Prabhaa Hain|| Su Jougad(i) Sudhaa Hain||125||
translation: That Thine is the Most Powerful Glow. That Thou art ever united with all.125.

gurmukhi: ਸਦੈਵੰ ਸਰੂਪ ਹੈਂ || ਅਭੇਦੀ ਅਨੂਪ ਹੈਂ ||
translation: That Thou art Eternal Entity. That Thou art undivided and unparalleled.

gurmukhi: ਸਮਸਤੋਪਰਾਜ ਹੈਂ || ਸਦਾ ਸਰਬ ਸਾਜ ਹੈਂ ||੧੨੬||
transliteration: Samasto Paraaj Hain|| Sadaa Sarab Saaj Hain||126||
translation: That Thou art the Creator of all. That Thou art ever the Ornamentation of all. 126.

gurmukhi: ਸਮਸਤੁਲ ਸਲਾਮ ਹੈਂ || ਸਦੈਵਲ ਅਕਾਮ ਹੈਂ ||
transliteration: Samastul Salaam Hain|| Sadaival Akaam Hain||
translation: That Thou art saluted by all. That Thou art ever the Desireless Lord.

gurmukhi: ਨਿ੍ਰਬਾਧ ਸਰੂਪ ਹੈਂ || ਅਗਾਧਿ ਹੈਂ ਅਨੂਪ ਹੈਂ ||੧੨੭||
transliteration: Nribaadh Saroophain|| Agaddh Hain Anoop Hain||127||
translation: That Thou art Invincible. That Thou art Impenetrable and Unparalleled Entity.127.
That Thou art Aum the primal Entity. That Thou art also without beginning.
That Thu art Bodyless and Nameless. That Thou art the Destroyer and Restorer of three modes. 128.
That Thou art the Destroyer of three gods and modes. That Thou art Immortal and Impenetrable.

transliteration: Soubhan Sarab Bhaage|| Su Sarabaa Anuraage||129||
translation: That Thy Writ of Destiny is for all. That Thou lovest all. 129.

gurmukhi: ਤਿ੍ਰਭੁਗਤ ਸਰੂਪ ਹੈਂ || ਅਛਿੱਜ ਹੈਂ ਅਛੂਤ ਹੈਂ ||
transliteration: Tribhougad Saroophain|| Achhijj Hain Achhoht Hain||
translation: That Thou art the Enjoyer Entity of three worlds. That Thou art Unbreakable and untouched.
